  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Waste workers recycling plastic in Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Solid waste is poorly managed in Bangladesh. Low value plastic is dumped in poorly managed landfill or discarded into the environment. Practical Action and RiverRecycle seek to transform the lives of informal waste workers by creating a new market for a stream of plastic waste which currently has no commercial value. The project introduces pyrolysis technology and integrates the extraction of plastics from rivers with municipal waste services creating new jobs and improving working conditions</narrative>
  </description>
